<body>
    <header>
        <h1><marquee height="45">Hotdog</marquee></h1>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>4 hotdog buns</li>
            <li>4 beef or pork hotdogs</li>
            <li>1/2 cup diced onions</li>
            <li>1/2 cup diced tomatoes</li>
            <li>1/4 cup pickle relish</li>
            <li>Mustard and ketchup for topping</li>
            <li>4 slices of your favorite cheese (optional)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Tags</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>lunch</li>
            <li>grilling</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Preheat a grill or stovetop grilling pan over medium heat.</li>
            <li>Grill the hotdogs until they are heated through and have grill marks, turning occasionally.</li>
            <li>While the hotdogs are grilling, toast the hotdog buns on the grill or in a toaster until lightly golden.</li>
            <li>Place a grilled hotdog into each bun.</li>
            <li>Top each hotdog with diced onions, diced tomatoes, pickle relish, and your choice of mustard and ketchup.</li>
            <li>If desired, add a slice of cheese on top of each hotdog.</li>
            <li>Serve the hotdogs immediately, and enjoy your delicious hotdog creation!</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

